Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language processing and specifically semantic role labeling. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes and evaluates several learning-based inference models. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with automated understanding of natural language. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with extracting information from text. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the least likely category, but still possible as the paper proposes and evaluates several feature extraction techniques.
